					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">For my ninja game, I based it vaguely on SMB, and had 2 full arrays of 16x13=208 (32 pixels at the top for HUD didn't need data)...and collision data doubled as metatiles for updating the PPU as I scrolled.<br /><br />So 2 arrays, because 2 nametables. And filled as I scrolled.</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://nesdoug.com" class="postlink">nesdoug.com</a> -- blog/tutorial on programming for the NES</div>
